  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个基础设施的调用流程图，核心是从Redis缓存开始，经过Ingress控制器，再到Etcd集群做决策，最后可能分发到工作节点。你先帮我起个头？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infra_RedisCache",
        "Infra_IngressController",
        "Infra_EtcdCluster",
        "Infra_WorkerNode"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，所以起点是Redis缓存。我想确认一下：Redis到Ingress控制器之间是什么操作？是简单的连接还是有具体的业务动作？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infra_RedisCache",
        "Infra_IngressController"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "是获取资金的操作，标注为\"Get money\"吧。然后Ingress控制器要访问Etcd集群做路由决策，这个决策点需要做成菱形判断节点。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infra_RedisCache",
        "Infra_IngressController",
        "Infra_EtcdCluster"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先把Redis和Ingress控制器连起来，标上\"Get money\"，然后把Etcd集群做成菱形决策节点。现在Redis→Ingress→Etcd这个主干有了。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infra_RedisCache",
        "Infra_IngressController",
        "Infra_EtcdCluster"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "Etcd这里需要三条分支出去，分别对应One、Two、Three三种决策结果。前两个还是回到Etcd集群本身做某种确认或同步，第三个要走到Worker节点去实际执行任务。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infra_EtcdCluster",
        "Infra_WorkerNode"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "确认一下：决策点C分出三条线，C→D标\"One\"，C→E标\"Two\"，C→F标\"Three\"，其中F是Worker节点。但D和E也是Etcd集群？这和C是同一个组件吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infra_EtcdCluster",
        "Infra_WorkerNode"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "对，D和E可以理解为Etcd集群的不同实例或副本，用于Leader选举后的同步确认。F则是真正的工作节点。这样画能表达清楚吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infra_EtcdCluster",
        "Infra_WorkerNode"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "明白了，我这就把三条分支加上，标注好One、Two、Three。现在整个流程从Redis到Ingress，经Etcd决策，再到三个后续节点，结构已经完整了。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infra_EtcdCluster",
        "Infra_WorkerNode"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "我看看……等等，B到C那条线，我们是不是忘了标操作？Redis到Ingress有\"Get money\"，但Ingress到Etcd好像光秃秃的。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infra_IngressController",
        "Infra_EtcdCluster"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "您说得对，我漏了。Ingress到Etcd的查询操作应该标什么？是\"Query\"还是\"Lookup\"？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infra_IngressController",
        "Infra_EtcdCluster"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "其实这里不用标，Ingress到Etcd是内部查询，保持无标签更简洁。我们保持现状就好，不用加文字。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infra_IngressController",
        "Infra_EtcdCluster"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 12,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "好的，保持B到C无标签。最终确认：Redis→Ingress(\"Get money\")→Etcd(菱形决策)→三条分支(One/Two/Three)，其中One和Two指向Etcd副本，Three指向Worker节点。这样对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infra_RedisCache",
        "Infra_IngressController",
        "Infra_EtcdCluster",
        "Infra_WorkerNode"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 13,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "完全正确，就是这个结构。可以定稿了。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infra_RedisCache",
        "Infra_IngressController",
        "Infra_EtcdCluster",
        "Infra_WorkerNode"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    }
